Vision: To become the global standard for service-based appointment scheduling, empowering independent professionals and simplifying client bookings worldwide.

Mission: To build a secure, scalable, and accessible platform that enables service providers to efficiently manage their schedules while providing clients with a seamless, intuitive booking experience.

Product: A comprehensive scheduling SaaS platform connecting tutors, coaches, consultants, and other service-based professionals with clients globally. Built with TypeScript + Java/Spring Boot, deployed on AWS, featuring full accessibility, internationalization, and enterprise-grade security.

Current Status: Day 1 of 140-Day Development Roadmap - Technical foundation being laid with simultaneous business entity formation.

