5.3 Pricing Strategy (Founder-Validated)
For Clients:
Free: Browse and book appointments

Premium Features: $4.99/month for advanced booking options

For Providers:
Tier	Price	Features	Target Users
Basic	Free	10 appointments/month	New providers
Professional	$14.99/month	Unlimited, video calls, file sharing	Full-time professionals
Business	$49.99/month	Team features, white-label, analytics	Agencies, schools
Founder's Pricing Research:

Willingness to Pay: $10-30/month (survey of 50 tutors)

Current Spending: $0-20/month on fragmented tools

Value Proposition: Save 10 hours/month = $450 value at $45/hour rate

