8. Technology Stack (Updated for Java/Spring Boot)
8.1 Complete Stack Architecture
text
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Frontend Layer                    │
│  • TypeScript + React + Vite                         │
│  • Playwright (E2E Testing)                         │
│  • SCSS with CSS Modules                             │
│  • i18next (Internationalization)                   │
│  • PWA Capabilities                                 │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            ↓ HTTPS/API
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  Backend Layer (Java)                │
│  • Java 17 + Spring Boot 3.1                        │
│  • Spring Security + JWT                            │
│  • Spring Data JPA (PostgreSQL)                     │
│  • Spring Data OpenSearch                           │
│  • Spring Cloud (future microservices)              │
│  • MapStruct (DTO mapping)                          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                Data Layer & Search                   │
│  • PostgreSQL 15 (Primary Database)                 │
│  • OpenSearch 2.11 (Search & Analytics)             │
│  • Debezium (Change Data Capture)                   │
│  • Redis (Caching)                                  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                Infrastructure Layer                  │
│  • AWS (EC2, RDS, OpenSearch Service)               │
│  • Docker + Docker Compose                          │
│  • GitHub Actions (CI/CD)                           │
│  • Prometheus + Grafana (Monitoring)                │
│  • Sentry (Error Tracking)                          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
8.2 Why Java/Spring Boot?
Enterprise Readiness: Battle-tested, scalable, secure

Talent Availability: Large pool of Java developers

Long-term Stability: Backward compatibility, long-term support

Performance: Excellent for high-concurrency scenarios

Ecosystem: Mature libraries for everything we need

8.3 PostgreSQL + OpenSearch Synergy
text
┌─────────────────────────┐    CDC via Debezium    ┌─────────────────────────┐
│                         │ ──────────────────────> │                         │
│   PostgreSQL (RDBMS)    │                         │   OpenSearch (Search)   │
│                         │ <────────────────────── │                         │
│  • User accounts        │    Search Results       │  • Full-text search     │
│  • Transactions         │                         │  • Analytics           │
│  • Complex joins        │                         │  • Aggregations        │
│  • ACID compliance      │                         │  • Real-time updates   │
└─────────────────────────┘                         └─────────────────────────┘
       Primary Source of Truth                           Search & Analytics
Use Cases:

PostgreSQL: User registration, payments, appointments (transactions)

OpenSearch: Provider search, analytics dashboards, autocomplete

